### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/health

### List videos
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/videos

### Create a video
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/videos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Salsa lesson summary",
  "sourceType": "youtube",
  "sourceUrl": "https://youtube.com/watch?v=abc123"
}
